                <meta property="og:title" content="ITV and startup announce Stamford hub, plan hundreds of jobs"/>
                    <meta property="og:description" content="Reality-show powerhouse ITV America will relocate a large portion of its operations to Stamford's South End and startup Wheelhouse Entertainment will set up in the same facility in a state-backed project expected to create about 450 jobs, officials announced Friday. 

The two companies would move into a vacant 90,000-square-foot building at 860 Canal St., where they would run operations including production, post-production and finance. The state is supporting the initiative with a $6 million loan to ITV America and a $3 million loan to Wheelhouse Entertainment. Partial loan forgiveness would be possible if certain job targets were met."/>
                                            <meta property="og:type" content="article"/>
